Name: Java Application Bundler 
Short Name: appbundler
URL: https://java.net/projects/appbundler
Version: 1.0
License: GPL-2.0

Description:
Packages a Java application as Mac app bundle.

See https://java.net/projects/appbundler/pages/Home 
and http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/jweb/packagingAppsForMac.html 
for related documentation.

Local Modifications:
Updated to use the fork from https://bitbucket.org/infinitekind/appbundler/ built at revision f715a34bff95 as follows:

1. Download the source code as a zip archive and extract.
2. Run `ant` from the top-level directory.
3. Copy the resulting /appbundler/bin/appbundler-1.0ea.jar file to this directory.
